{"tid":2247439,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–日常的心臟究竟攝取哪一種營養","createTime":"2020-10-17T23:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T22:50:12.000Z","uid":38861,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3a65b266748ebad86f42d8cadab81ed21b5dffb5","tid":2247439,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T23:03:03.000Z","msg":"由我們出世一刻起，心臟便不辭勞苦工作，將血液送至全身，沒有休息的一刻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hG2Bk3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhG2Bk3f.jpg&h=74cd102d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你又有沒有想過，心臟究竟係「食咩大㗎呢」?<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)有科學家為了解答這個問題，找來110個病人(87個心臟正常，23個心臟出現問題)，請示測試者禁食一晚，然後再進行全身麻醉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3ReR9Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3ReR9Y.png&h=021bde74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在麻醉期間的1小時裡，分別抽取對應部份血管的血液，從而計算出心臟及腳部的新陳代謝狀況(Ref1)。<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)綜合所有證據顯示，心臟同腳部均會大量吸收Ketone Bodies，Acetate及Glutamate。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhxQ9WF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhxQ9WF.png&h=308624d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，腳部會選擇性地吸收飽和脂肪酸，而放出非飽和脂肪酸，<br />\n但心臟莫論飽和與否均會全數吸收，其中脂肪酸更成為了它能量來源70%有多。<br />\n<br />\n某程度上可以說心臟是「食脂肪大的」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，心臟同腳部均有釋放氨基酸的跡象，顯示細胞的蛋白質一直處於分解狀態，而心臟其速度比腳部快10倍有多。<br />\n<br />\n對比健康心臟及心臟出現問題的病人，出現問題的心臟會吸取更多的Ketone Bodies及增加氨基酸的釋放數量。<br />\n<br />\n究竟吸取更多的Ketone Bodies和增加氨基酸釋放量是為了阻擋心臟出現進一步惡化，還是因為出現問題所致而成，這方面還需要進一步的研究。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPROHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=4120ee0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPROHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=0524af72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPROHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=e76fe15c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/370/6514/364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F370%2F6514%2F364&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPROHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=7e14a004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/370/6514/364</a>"},{"pid":"ead69531736a76087e5a9efbb061d5ee6f820fc9","tid":2247439,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T23:10:26.000Z","msg":"G chi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2cde9118f1c4b1b83861add28ddf880d3bc864","tid":2247439,"uid":34881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T00:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgm